OL,3,CBody of a missing 18-year-old found in
OL,4,Criver
OL,6,FA body has been found in a river after
OL,7,Fa multi-agency search for an 18-year-
OL,8,Fold missing man.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FRiver Wye at Glasbury in Powys on
OL,12,FTuesday night (June 30) at
OL,13,Fapproximately 6:30pm, after reports of
OL,14,Fa teenager entering the water before
OL,15,Fbeing reported as missing.
OL,17,FDyfed-Powys Police, Mid and West Wales
OL,18,FFire and Rescue Service, Mountain
OL,19,FRescue and the National Police Air
OL,20,FService were involved in the search.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/2
