OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1783521457
OL,3,CBody of a missing 18-year-old found in
OL,4,Criver
OL,6,FPolice remain in the area and have
OL,7,Fasked the public to avoid the area.
OL,9,FA Dyfed-Powys Police spokes person
OL,10,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with his
OL,11,Ffamily and loved ones at this
OL,12,Fdifficult time.
OL,14,F"Emergency services remain in the area
OL,15,Fand ask that members of the public
OL,16,Fstay away while enquiries continue."
OL,18,FThe family of the teenager have been
OL,19,Finformed and are being supported.
